    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Standards Are Being Lowered</strong>&mdash;Christian parents are giving way to the world-loving propensities of their children. They open the door to amusements which from principle they once prohibited.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 119, 1899\" data-link=\"14064.4934001\">Manuscript 119, 1899</span>.</span></a></sup>",
