    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>The Secret of Guarding the Children From Worldly Attractions</strong>&mdash;How many parents are lamenting the fact that they cannot keep their children at home, that they have no love for home! At an early age they have a desire for the company of strangers; and as soon as they are old <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"530\"></span> enough, they break away from that which appears to them to be bondage and unreasonable restraint and will neither heed a mother&apos;s prayers nor a father&apos;s counsels. Investigation would generally reveal that the sin lay at the door of the parents. They have not made home what it ought to be&mdash;attractive, pleasant, radiant with the sunshine of kind words, pleasant looks, and true love.",
